<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Staff Invitation - DentalFlow</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .invitation-header {
            color: #2563eb;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .details-box {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details-title {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .details-list {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .details-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #475569;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #1d4ed8;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
            color: #92400e;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            {{#if companyLogo}}
            <img src="{{companyLogo}}" alt="{{companyName}}" class="logo">
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="invitation-header">ðŸŽ‰ You're Invited to Join DentalFlow!</h2>
            
            <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
            
            <p>You have been invited to join <strong>{{clinicName}}</strong> as a staff member on the DentalFlow platform.</p>
            
            <div class="details-box">
                <h3 class="details-title">Your Role Details:</h3>
                <ul class="details-list">
                    <li><strong>Role:</strong> {{role}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Clinic:</strong> {{clinicName}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Invited by:</strong> {{invitedBy}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Invitation Date:</strong> {{invitationDate}}</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>To get started, you'll need to create your account and set up your password. Click the button below to begin:</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{activationLink}}" class="button">Activate Your Account</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #2563eb;">{{activationLink}}</p>
            
            <div class="warning">
                <strong>Important:</strong> This invitation link will expire in {{expiryTime}} for security reasons. Please activate your account as soon as possible.
            </div>
            
            <p>Once you activate your account, you'll be able to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access the clinic's patient management system</li>
                <li>Manage appointments and schedules</li>
                <li>View and update patient records</li>
                <li>Collaborate with other staff members</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact your clinic administrator.</p>
            
            <p>Welcome to the team!<br>
            The {{companyName}} Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>{{companyAddress}}</p>
            {{#if unsubscribeLink}}
            <p><a href="{{unsubscribeLink}}">Unsubscribe</a></p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 